{"tid":365121,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本土KOL仇思達而家連左膠乳鴿區諾軒都要痴","createTime":"2017-08-19T03:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T08:41:51.000Z","uid":78253,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"876ce6fd501090b3eaa567e74a4abf910d28739c","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/114150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F114150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bf91abdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息係仇狗買枱叫區諾軒嚟<br />\n笑死喇，呢條友又搵新宿主寄生<br />\n話自己係反泛民先鋒嘅要痴返日鬧夜鬧嘅左膠泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣召集人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仇狗咁大方<br />\n有無叫返教主十一上貢俾返民陣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起嚟區諾軒早過佢N年反熱<br />\n佢15年一個區嘅票都贏哂咁多隻熱狗加埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講咩live聽眾數字添喇<br />\n果時仇狗仲夾緊熱血日日夜夜抹黑區諾軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(分身定益友快D推po啦)"},{"pid":"485e69ae02f8d122f5057be2323400d1b202e55a","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"坐等益友(分身)入嚟鬧我係水泥隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be7aaf8af987b554ee42bcaeaba216c38136097","tid":365121,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"完全唔想理呢條垃圾"},{"pid":"101468529171861d18e05a8bdc1825ec80f5fac6","tid":365121,"uid":48157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eb4d9f36e1161bb1ff9c98a646d4cabfa7cb890","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泥隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n益友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a01591f3464a97807603d825ac5ceb655c149","tid":365121,"uid":65649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"叫得人十一個d on9仔，唔係水泥隊就係弱撚智"},{"pid":"9478f0c15362ca1fd5dd5cfcdcfb71cdc093f1c9","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫得人十一個d on9仔，唔係水泥隊就係弱撚智</blockquote><br />\n你話咩十一呀<br />\n仇狗衰十一呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗唔洗衝出嚟柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解次次鬧仇狗嘅po都見到你喺度呀<br />\n由一開始打熱狗果陣就明踩暗幫護住仇狗話佢係主力<br />\n到而家熱狗衰哂喇就出動逢人必話水泥隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292db6036deec53aead7da649386403b81c16210","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全唔想理呢條垃圾</blockquote><br />\n仲信佢果D益友就真係弱智<br />\n條社運寄生蟲不講立場<br />\n見邊個上位就痴埋去要人打上嚟乜乜乜<br />\n人哋失勢就開咪踩多兩腳搏hit rate<br />\neg. Ray Wong，容癌，青政，泰博不計其數<br />\n熱狗惡D，就要教主首肯先可以開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家發現全世界都俾佢鬧勻<br />\n本土大勢已去<br />\n就要痴返最淋善嘅泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但投票牠還是會投民建聯的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(期待佢幾時同眾志，小麗，朱迪扮fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"faa057c83f6c353a9c2f1bb57e8db0da7bc57e17","tid":365121,"uid":2076,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"熱狗個爐愈圍愈細<br />\n繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082a56dd25e40e35820bc32b7d2db9e6516d448a","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗個爐愈圍愈細<br />\n繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好無聊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家熱狗失勢就將所有鬧仇狗嘅射哂俾水泥隊<br />\n做乜唔鬧我係港大幫呀<br />\n鬧我係王俊傑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9f427d2f13a700af5409b6da382e6742eaa3cd","tid":365121,"uid":56428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"而家係區生痴本土派喎。 搞清楚主場未呀"},{"pid":"643418c873219084214e866a487944ab84e82fe9","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家係區生痴本土派喎。 搞清楚主場未呀</blockquote><br />\n區諾軒一早搵過游B上花生台啦<br />\n區生一向與人為善個喎<br />\n開火嘅人鬧返人哋想痴埋嚟都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n李柱銘班大狀幫梁天琦佢地一定都係為咗痴埋去本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42e1509aed03d17a223082aada37b34101e391e","tid":365121,"uid":62929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"本民前同港大好似冇人去台慶<br />\n<br />\n睇仇狗幾時又做大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceef5d2c61032dbdf05c852825504a161858f73d","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本民前同港大好似冇人去台慶<br />\n<br />\n睇仇狗幾時又做大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好慘<br />\n只可同俾佢屌咗咁多年嘅泛民圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8030af7c61f4c7de4aeee1c7979331a51e7e7ed","tid":365121,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"兩邊都咁廢，打和啦 super"},{"pid":"4a980b7592d08997aa6585b32acd345795ce670f","tid":365121,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"班益友係facebook話「就算政見不同 大家始終係反共 何必落井下石」<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地唔記得有人左膠 泛民 熱狗 乜柒都屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365db08eeb8ec8b038e05915edfdbd8d119e8933","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班益友係facebook話「就算政見不同 大家始終係反共 何必落井下石」<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地唔記得有人左膠 泛民 熱狗 乜柒都屌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神駒向益友下達之最高指令<br />\n碌撚無哂政治能量，係時候轉駄咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60abd748fe476ae75489d82ee4562ca5fad60f6f","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩邊都咁廢，打和啦 super</blockquote><br />\n仇狗同熱狗？<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec6fe81833cd70346511cc2eb73d12271a1e84e","tid":365121,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"發覺神駒同毓民都幾似"},{"pid":"4d60f6b771e87a5626d1b0567f0ef8de80c0618f","tid":365121,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺神駒同毓民都幾似</blockquote><br />\n傳聞話係接班人"},{"pid":"4baecdf3a3691f57e29a7df3281675ed45ac60ed","tid":365121,"uid":65649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱狗個爐愈圍愈細<br />\n繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好無聊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家熱狗失勢就將所有鬧仇狗嘅射哂俾水泥隊<br />\n做乜唔鬧我係港大幫呀<br />\n鬧我係王俊傑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你讀閪到港大咩，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，神駒屌熱狗係有證有據，呢部份你咁都有位入佢？佢又唔會去選舉，又冇叫人課金，又冇靠社運掠水，對佢既指控仲停留係n年前高登d小學雞惡作劇，隻錶壞撚左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2017啦依家<br />\n<br />\n為屌而屌你覺得有意思咪有意思囉，你地咁撚關心退休廢老同隻馬，不如諗下你主人熱狗3年後仲有冇機會選到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe50817c63f40c4a3b32eb8132181fc076bf27b","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發覺神駒同毓民都幾似</blockquote><br />\n傳聞話係接班人</blockquote><br />\n靈童去到第幾代了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce52a9c60621d66fb4cf05b9b42bf2b3009407b","tid":365121,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>熱狗個爐愈圍愈細<br />\n繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好無聊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家熱狗失勢就將所有鬧仇狗嘅射哂俾水泥隊<br />\n做乜唔鬧我係港大幫呀<br />\n鬧我係王俊傑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你讀閪到港大咩，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，神駒屌熱狗係有證有據，呢部份你咁都有位入佢？佢又唔會去選舉，又冇叫人課金，又冇靠社運掠水，對佢既指控仲停留係n年前高登d小學雞惡作劇，隻錶壞撚左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2017啦依家<br />\n<br />\n為屌而屌你覺得有意思咪有意思囉，你地咁撚關心退休廢老同隻馬，不如諗下你主人熱狗3年後仲有冇機會選到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年幾之前你主人最中意屌人乜嘢呀<br />\n社毛人力狗鴿毛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣佢仲同熱狗稱兄道弟緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都無講佢以前高登點點點就驚到瀨咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff647543cce184ef55589b0f2a678765397f4c3","tid":365121,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T08:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>熱狗個爐愈圍愈細<br />\n繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好無聊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家熱狗失勢就將所有鬧仇狗嘅射哂俾水泥隊<br />\n做乜唔鬧我係港大幫呀<br />\n鬧我係王俊傑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你讀閪到港大咩，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，神駒屌熱狗係有證有據，呢部份你咁都有位入佢？佢又唔會去選舉，又冇叫人課金，又冇靠社運掠水，對佢既指控仲停留係n年前高登d小學雞惡作劇，隻錶壞撚左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2017啦依家<br />\n<br />\n為屌而屌你覺得有意思咪有意思囉，你地咁撚關心退休廢老同隻馬，不如諗下你主人熱狗3年後仲有冇機會選到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年幾之前你主人最中意屌人乜嘢呀<br />\n社毛人力狗鴿毛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣佢仲同熱狗稱兄道弟緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都無講佢以前高登點點點就驚到瀨咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁預撚到老千，依家知道左真面目去反擊有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n屌又嘈唔屌又嘈，成日咩高登咩咩咩，講d出黎聽下有幾咁有公共性同柒好冇？<br />\n<br />\n打幾隻字冇頭冇尾就想蒙混過關，慳d啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f151edd5c19e4e35c8f0c3cd8a92f271e94f2362